import React from "react";
import Tabs from "react-bootstrap/Tabs";
import Tab from "react-bootstrap/Tab";
import Form from "react-bootstrap/Form";
import Button from "react-bootstrap/Button";
import Row from "react-bootstrap/Row";
import Col from "react-bootstrap/Col";
import FloatingLabel from "react-bootstrap/FloatingLabel";
import Modal from "react-bootstrap/Modal";
const AddProject = (show, onHide) => {
  return (
    <Modal.Dialog show={show} onHide={onHide}>
      <Modal.Header closeButton>
        <Modal.Title>Add Project</Modal.Title>
      </Modal.Header>

      <Modal.Body>
        <Form>
          <Row>
            <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="clientName">
              <Form.Label>Client Name</Form.Label>
              <Form.Control />
            </Form.Group>
          </Row>
          <Tabs defaultActiveKey="basic">
            <Tab eventKey="basic" title="Basic">
              <Row>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="clientNick">
                  <Form.Label>Client Nick</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="email">
                  <Form.Label>Email address</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control />
                </Form.Group>
              </Row>
              <Row>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="website">
                  <Form.Label>Website</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="billingRate">
                  <Form.Label>Default Billing Rate</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control />
                </Form.Group>
              </Row>
            </Tab>

            <Tab eventKey="details" title="Details">
              <Row>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="address1">
                  <Form.Label>Address1</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="address2">
                  <Form.Label>Address2</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control />
                </Form.Group>
              </Row>
              <Row>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="country">
                  <Form.Label>Country</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Select aria-label="Default select example">
                    <option>Open this select menu</option>
                    <option value="1">One</option>
                    <option value="2">Two</option>
                    <option value="3">Three</option>
                  </Form.Select>{" "}
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="city">
                  <Form.Label>City</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control />
                </Form.Group>
              </Row>
              <Row>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="state">
                  <Form.Label>State</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="zipcode">
                  <Form.Label>Zipcode</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control />
                </Form.Group>
              </Row>
              <Row>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="telephone1">
                  <Form.Label>Telephone1</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="telephone2">
                  <Form.Label>Telephone2</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control />
                </Form.Group>
              </Row>
              <Row>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="fax">
                  <Form.Label>Fax</Form.Label>
                  <Form.Control />
                </Form.Group>
              </Row>
            </Tab>

            <Tab eventKey="notes" title="Notes">
              <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="notes">
                <FloatingLabel
                  controlId="floatingTextarea"
                  label="Notes"
                  className="mb-3"
                >
                  <Form.Control
                    as="textarea"
                    placeholder="Leave a comment here"
                  />{" "}
                </FloatingLabel>{" "}
              </Form.Group>
            </Tab>
            <Tab eventKey="billing" title="Billing">
              <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicCheckbox">
                <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Check " />
              </Form.Group>
            </Tab>
          </Tabs>
        </Form>
      </Modal.Body>

      <Modal.Footer>
        <Button variant="primary">Add Client</Button>
        <Button variant="secondary">Close</Button>
      </Modal.Footer>
    </Modal.Dialog>
  );
};

export default AddProject;
